- This demonstrates the use of local and global variables
-
- Assign this script to a pair of buttons.  Watch how the global variable is shared
- and the local variable isn't
-
- clear the stack
RPN_EVAL clst 
- Now get the global variable a and increment it
RPN_EVAL <G a 1 + >G a 
- Now get the local variable b and increment it
RPN_EVAL <L b 1 + > b
- look at the local and global variables
RPN_EVAL view_l view_g

